STATE OF FLORIDA, on the Relation of L. Knabb Construction Co., a Corporation, v. J. M. LEE, as Comptroller of the State of Florida. 22 So. (2nd) 811

June Term, 1945

July 20, 1945 En Bane Keen, Allen & O’Kelley, for relator. J. Tom Watson, Attorney General and George M. Powell, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent,. PER CURIAM:

The motion to quash the alternative writ is denied- on authority of State ex rel. Russell Badgett et al., v. J. M. Lee, Comptroller, filed this day.

CHAPMAN, C. J., TERRELL, BROWN, BUFORD, THOMAS, ADAMS and SEBRING, JJ., concur.
